528
00:20:36,170 --> 00:20:37,170
No need. Go on.

529
00:20:37,340 --> 00:20:37,970
Mr. Cheng!

530
00:20:38,850 --> 00:20:39,610
Mr. Cheng.

531
00:20:39,730 --> 00:20:41,120
Have you signed the confession?

532
00:20:41,250 --> 00:20:41,790
I want you

533
00:20:41,790 --> 00:20:42,800
to clear Shuai's name.

534
00:20:42,800 --> 00:20:43,680
Clear his name?

535
00:20:44,350 --> 00:20:45,780
That comes at a price.

536
00:20:50,280 --> 00:20:51,370
Mr. Cheng!

537
00:21:06,310 --> 00:21:07,650
According to The Great Ming Code,

538
00:21:08,250 --> 00:21:09,090
Shuai Jiamo's crime

539
00:21:09,090 --> 00:21:10,140
will get him flogged 30 times

540
00:21:10,140 --> 00:21:11,190
